<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf3d9c55-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11262"><num value="11262">§ 11262.</num><heading> Dissemination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director of the National Center for Health Services Research and Health Care Technology Assessment shall disseminate the results of research conducted under this part to appropriate professional entities and to the public.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf3d9c56-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/660/tIX/s935">Pub. L. 99–660, title IX, § 935</ref>, formerly § 948, <date date="1986-11-14">Nov. 14, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3812">100 Stat. 3812</ref>; renumbered § 935, <ref href="/us/pl/100/607/tI/s142/c/2/B">Pub. L. 100–607, title I, § 142(c)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="1988-11-04">Nov. 4, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/3057">102 Stat. 3057</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
